560
00:50:10,320 --> 00:50:11,990
.. Nearly a billion years.

561
00:50:12,040 --> 00:50:13,830
Argh!

562
00:50:13,880 --> 00:50:16,470
".. And when the entire
mountain is chiselled away,

563
00:50:16,520 --> 00:50:20,990
"the first second of
