564
00:50:21,040 --> 00:50:22,980
HE GASPS FOR AIR

565
00:50:24,160 --> 00:50:25,510
.. Well over a billion years.

566
00:50:25,560 --> 00:50:26,990
Argh!

567
00:50:27,040 --> 00:50:30,840
You must think that's
a hell of a long time.

568
00:50:31,640 --> 00:50:33,910
.. Two billion years.

569
00:50:35,200 --> 00:50:37,870
Personally, I think that's a hell of a...

