00:51:47,240 --> 00:51:49,710
LIGHT FOOTSTEPS APPROACH

583
00:51:56,400 --> 00:51:57,470
Go to the city.

584
00:51:57,520 --> 00:51:59,510
Find somebody important.

585
00:51:59,560 --> 00:52:01,990
Tell them, I'm back.

586
00:52:02,040 --> 00:52:04,910
Tell them, I know what they did,

587
00:52:04,960 --> 00:52:07,030
and I'm on my way.

588
00:52:08,080 --> 00:52:10,830
And if they ask you who I am,

589
00:52:10,880 --> 00:52:13,980
tell them, I came the long way round.

590
00:52:33,320 --> 00:52:36,320
You can probably still hear me...

591
00:52:37,040 --> 00:52:39,910
.. so just between ourselves...

592
00:52:40,480 --> 00:52:43,190
.. you've got the prophecy wrong.

593
00:52:43,240 --> 00:52:45,350
The Hybrid is not half Dalek.

594
00:52:45,400 --> 00:52:48,470
Nothing is half Dalek. The
Daleks would never allow that.

595
00:52:48,520 --> 00:52:51,990
The Hybrid destined to conquer Gallifrey

596
00:52:52,040 --> 00:52:54,510
and stand in its ruins...

597
00:52:58,840 --> 00:53:00,480
.. is me.

598
00:53:31,520 --> 00:53:34,230
The Hybrid. I think it's
time to tell the truth.

599
00:53:34,280 --> 00:53:36,350
I heard the Doctor had come home.

600
00:53:36,400 --> 00:53:37,950
One so loves fireworks.

601
00:53:38,000 --> 00:53:39,710
What's he up to?

602
00:53:39,760 --> 00:53:42,630
The Hybrid is a creature
thought to be crossbred

603
00:53:42,680 --> 00:53:44,190
from two warrior races.

604
00:53:44,240 --> 00:53:45,510
I know I went too far.

605
00:53:45,560 --> 00:53:48,470
You have broken every
code you ever lived by.

606
00:53:48,520 --> 00:53:50,350
On my command!

607
00:53:50,400 --> 00:53:51,550
Is it true?

608
00:53:51,600 --> 00:53:53,070
- She's my friend.
- Fire!

